# Timeweb Cloud credentials for provisioning the ds-platform deploy slice (DSO-100).
# Copy to `infra/deploy/.env` (gitignored) and fill in. NEVER commit real values.
# Same Timeweb account as bbm; project-scope `ds-platform` (own state/token).

# The twc Terraform provider reads THIS variable:
TWC_TOKEN=

# Convenience mirror (some scripts read this name); keep in sync with TWC_TOKEN.
# TIMEWEB_CLOUD_TOKEN=
